         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">26/7/87. ¶  ¶ With this post I am sending you, esteemed Mr Stephani, a number of lithograms that Mr Bastow has produced of Tasmanian Jungermanniaceae. ¶  I have asked him to send me the originals, so ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">87.07.26</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Franz Stephani</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Conservatoire et Jardin botanique, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">26/7/87.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit dieser Post sende ich Ihnen, geehrter Herr Stephani, eine Anzahl Lithogrammata, die Herr Bastow von Tasmanischen Jungermanniaceen geliefert hat. Ich habe ihn aufgefordert, mir die Originale zu senden, damit Ihnen auch solche für critische Revision zugänglich würden. So wird er seine Addenda Ihnen auch wohl durch mich zuwenden.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie ehrend der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">26/7/87.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With this post I am sending you, esteemed Mr Stephani, a number of lithograms that Mr Bastow has produced of Tasmanian <name key="Jungermanniaceae">Jungermanniaceae</name>.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Probably some or all of the figures accompanying Bastow (1888), which was read in July 1887. They are not cited in Stephani (1889).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> I have asked him to send me the originals, so that they also would be accessible to you for critical revision. Thus he will let you have his addenda probably also through me.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Jungermanniaceae">Jungermanniaceae</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
